channel.title: SRL Paint Script
channel.description: Well, this isn't really a request, but theres a script that I saw a long time ago, pretty much, you would open up paint, and the script would paint 'SRL' in big, green letters using the pencil tool. I have no idea who wrote it, what it was called, or when it was released. :D Well if anyone's got it, or another script like it, could'ja pm it to me? :cool:
